Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:39.68,English,,0,0,0,,and by showing the truth, I make you a better person.\N{\rChinese}并且通过展示真相，我让你们成为更好的人。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.88,English,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I think a just punishment would be a penchant.\N{\rChinese}因此我想要点儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:49.10,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? You guys should pay me to retire in peace.\N{\rChinese}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:51.38,English,,0,0,0,,But, you know what?\N{\rChinese}但你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:54.36,English,,0,0,0,,I'm a generous and forgiving individual.\N{\rChinese}我是一位慷慷大方的好人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:57.64,English,,0,0,0,,Therefore, if you don't want to give me a pension, I will understand.\N{\rChinese}因此我可以给你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.02,0:17:01.86,English,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I am willing to pay a small fine, okay?\N{\rChinese}因此，我愿意支付一点小罚款，好的？
