Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:31.48,English,,0,0,0,,And The Republic is the most famous of Plato's work.\N{\rChinese}《共和国》是柏拉图的作品中最著名的。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:34.46,English,,0,0,0,,It is arguably the greatest work of Western philosophy.\N{\rChinese}它可以说是西方哲学的最著名作。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:38.78,English,,0,0,0,,And many today consider The Republic the greatest book ever written.\N{\rChinese}多位今日认为《共和国》是史上最伟大的著作。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:40.72,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? There are people in this world who have written a lot of great books.\N{\rChinese}好吧，世界里有些人写过多种大作，但却没能写出《共和国》。”
