Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.06,0:28:06.08,English,,0,0,0,,Okay? It's a source of all truth.\N{\rChinese}好吧？它是所有真相的源头。
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.18,0:28:08.72,English,,0,0,0,,It is the truth. It's called the form of the good.\N{\rChinese}它是真相。它被称为“好”的形态。
