Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.92,0:28:27.18,English,,0,0,0,,And justice. Okay?\N{\rChinese}和正义。好？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.24,0:28:29.38,English,,0,0,0,,And there are others. Okay? But these are the main ones.\N{\rChinese}还有其他的。好？但这些是主要的。
